R13AUD.original: ~z~I didn't have no scars until you arrived.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你来之前我身上一道疤都没有。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Hey, I hear you know Florian Cravic. Where is he?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~喂，听说你认识Florian Cravic。他在哪儿？

R13AUD.original: ~z~Roman? You put on a few vanity pounds.
~z~I'll take you down just like I did at that last tournament.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我会像上次对局那样击败你的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Florian? You used to work in the abattoir?
~z~You think we're stupid, Talbot? We have been here already.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~当我们傻的吗，Talbot？这里才刚来过。

R13AUD.original: ~z~He wasn't the one I was looking for.
~z~It's Bernie now. After I came here, I wanted a complete change. So I became Bernie Crane.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~现在是Bernie了。来这儿以后咱就想告别过去，所以咱成了Bernie Crane。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Last thing I heard, you was itching to whack this guy? Must be some heavy shit.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~之前你不是还说很想干死这个人吗？那估计是个大岔子了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Ummm. I really don't recognize this. I can't help you from here I'm afraid.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~呃，这里我真不认识。在这儿我恐怕帮不了你了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Anything for you, cousin. Just name it. You want some women? I met this...
R13AUD.translated: ~z~赴汤蹈火在所不辞，堂弟。开口吧。你想找女人吗？我这儿有个...

R13AUD.original: ~z~Well, I'm a lifestyle coach, and I teach an aerobics class...
R13AUD.translated: ~z~咱现在是个养生教练，上课教有氧运动的内容...

R13AUD.original: ~z~Florian has moved on from what happened to you, you should move on too.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Florian has moved on from what happened to you, you should move on too.

R13AUD.original: ~z~What you do, cousin? You should have followed his direction.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你在干嘛，堂弟？你应该照他说的走的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Hey, slow down. I can't see the turns.
~z~I'm sorry about the fat thing... you're still kind of cute.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~说你肥咱很抱歉...你还挺可爱的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Cousin, Talbot is dead. We needed him to take us to Florian.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Cousin, Talbot is dead. We needed him to take us to Florian.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Oh, I started working out... you know, toned up the, er...
R13AUD.translated: ~z~噢，咱开始健身了...你也知道，壮实了一下，呃...

R13AUD.original: ~z~I'm not having Talbot sit on my knee. Get a bigger car.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~I'm not having Talbot sit on my knee. Get a bigger car.

R13AUD.original: ~z~I will find out where he is, and I will make him answer for his actions.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~I will find out where he is, and I will make him answer for his actions.

R13AUD.original: ~z~I... I... I heard he was still in Europe, or Switzerland, or somewhere...
R13AUD.translated: ~z~咱...咱...咱听说他还在欧洲，瑞士，或者哪里...

R13AUD.original: ~z~Shit, NB, I haven't got time to sit here while you fuck about.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, NB, I haven't got time to sit here while you fuck about.

R13AUD.original: ~z~We were so close, cousin, so close. I will see you soon.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我们差点就找到了，堂兄，就差一点。回头见。

R13AUD.original: ~z~We know now that it was him. I need to be alone now, Roman.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~现在我们知道是他干的了。我要一个人静静，Roman。

R13AUD.original: ~z~I worry for you, NB. Sometimes you just got to let the hate go.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我很替你担心，NB。有时候还是得放下往日仇恨。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Oh yeah, I should probably say, you ain't gonna get those ten Gs from Talbot.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~哦对了，有件事我得说，那一万你没法从Talbot手里拿回来了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Ahh, Roman's dead. I am not going to fill out a police report.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~啊，Roman死了，我可不想去填警方报告。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Sure, I'll see you later then. Call me, okay?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~好的，我们之后见。有空联系，好吧？

R13AUD.original: ~z~Ease up a little, big fella. I can't see when you're going that fast.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~慢一点，大哥。你开那么快我不认路。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Talbot, I know him. I came up against him in a few tournaments. Small world.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Talbot，我认识。打牌的时候对上过几次。世界真小。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Niko, that was unfortunate. There will be some other way to find Florian.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，太不幸了。总会有其它能找Florian的法子的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~This is too bad, cousin. Maybe we find Florian another day.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~这太糟了，堂弟。也许我们还是改天再找Florian吧。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Sure, I'll see you later then. Call me, okay?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~好的，我们之后见。有空打给我，好吧？

R13AUD.original: ~z~He doesn't act well under pressure, NB. Beat him a little.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~一有压力他就演不下去了，NB。稍微揍一顿。

R13AUD.original: ~z~So, it was Darko Brevic who betrayed you. Now you know. You should relax.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~So, it was Darko Brevic who betrayed you. Now you know. You should relax.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Don't fuck around, Talbot. I have seen this block before.
~z~I will be calm when we find Florian. See you, cousin.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~I will be calm when we find Florian. See you, cousin.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Bryce Dawkins? But he's so into family values!
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Bryce Dawkins？那他还整天讲家庭观念！

R13AUD.original: ~z~Alright already. There's a guy I know, likes to be called Florian Cravic at... um... certain moments.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~够了够了。我是认识个人，好像是叫Florian Cravic...呃...偶尔会这么叫他。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Roman. Can you do me a favor?
~z~We're looking for a guy named Talbot Daniels. Hangs out in the Triangle.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我们要找的是一个叫Talbot Daniels的人。经常在Triangle出没。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Niko, be calm. We will find Florian soon.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Niko, be calm. We will find Florian soon.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Now that I know it was Darko, he is all I will be able to think about.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Now that I know it was Darko, he is all I will be able to think about.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Come up with me Roman. I cannot do this alone.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~和我一起上来，Roman。这我不能一个人去。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Follow his direction or we will never get there, cousin.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Follow his direction or we will never get there, cousin.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Ummm, I might be lost but keep going and I'll see if I can get there.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Ummm, I might be lost but keep going and I'll see if I can get there.

R13AUD.original: ~z~We aren't going to find this place if you keep messing around.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~We aren't going to find this place if you keep messing around.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Okay, I cannot work at this speed. No siree.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我说，开太快我认不出路。完全不行。

R13AUD.original: ~z~~c~Florian! I'm here for you, asshole. Open the door!~s~
~z~And he's in politics... he's the deputy mayor.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~而且他还从政...他就是副市长。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Get out of here. I don't want to see you at any more tournaments either.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Get out of here. I don't want to see you at any more tournaments either.

R13AUD.original: ~z~You know, if this fucks up, the bad shit's coming down on my head.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你要知道，要是这次搞砸了，又得轮到我遭罪。

R13AUD.original: ~z~but then I heard that you had joined the circus so information can be unreliable.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~不过咱也听说过你加入了马戏团，所以消息不一定靠谱。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Stay right there, Talbot. Don't think you can push me around.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~乖乖站好，Talbot。别想着你能从我这儿逃了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Niko, you didn't need to kill him. He brought us here.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，没必要杀了他的。他都把路带到了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Easy there, man. You need to go slow if I'm gonna be able to get you there.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~开慢点，老兄。你不开慢我没法带你到地方。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Get in the car. You're showing us where Florian lives.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Get in the car. You're showing us where Florian lives.

R13AUD.original: ~z~He's into me for about ten Gs, he says he might know something about Florian Cravic.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~他找到我开口就要了一万，他说他可能知道Florian Cravic的下落。

R13AUD.original: ~z~What are you doing, Talbot? You take us around in circles?
~z~You kill the wrong guy and his friends will fuck with me to get to you.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你一杀错人，他的朋友就会来找我麻烦，好找到你。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Can't say I'm entirely sure about this, head on though.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Can't say I'm entirely sure about this, head on though.

R13AUD.original: ~z~I think I may have found the man I've been looking for.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我可能找到我在找的那个人了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Can we stop with the fat jokes, Florian?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我们能不开关于肥的玩笑了吗，Florian？

R13AUD.original: ~z~Niko? What the hell are you doing here?
~z~I mean, you fuck up and I take the shit.
~z~We must go slowly to find this place, NB.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我们得开慢点才能找到地方，NB。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Don't think you're going anywhere, Talbot. I'm going to go easy on you for now. But if you push me, you're in big trouble.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你哪儿都别想去，Talbot。我现在先对你客气点，不过你要是逼我，那你麻烦就大了。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Well screw you, Niko Bellic and fatty Roman!
~z~Ray Boccino, the cockroach mobster, he knows a man who might know Florian Cravic.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Ray Boccino，那个狡诈的黑社会，他知道一个可能认识Florian Cravic的人。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Stop fucking about and get to this place, cousin.
~z~He's moved on from what happened to you, you should've moved on too. What are you going to do?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~他已经走出那件事了，你也该往前走。现在你什么打算？

R13AUD.original: ~z~I think I can get us there if we keep going.
~z~Your days of searching are over, my friend. This guy should point you in the right direction.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你找人的日子结束了，我的朋友。这个人应该能给你带路。

R13AUD.original: ~z~This is impossible when you're going this fast. I can't see any of the turnoffs.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你开这么快就找不着了，我连路口都看不见。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Of course they would have. Look at your gambling career. What was I thinking?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~当然是早晚会了。看看你的赌博事业吧，我在想什么呢？

R13AUD.original: ~z~Come on, NB. You think I keep this figure by walking? Go get us a car.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~拜托，NB。我要是肯走路还会是这副样子吗？去弄辆车来。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Not too good either. I don't think I've seen him win a hand.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~牌技也不好。我好像就没见他赢过一次。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Shit Nicky, I was counting on that vig.
~z~I needed to warm up. Let's go.
~z~Come on, NB. We won't ever find Florian unless you follow these directions.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Come on, NB. We won't ever find Florian unless you follow these directions.

R13AUD.original: ~z~He may not be here in Liberty City, but he's still out there.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~他可能不在自由城，但他一定还活着。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Too bad, chief. I did what I could.
~z~Okay, I don't recognize this but keep going.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Okay, I don't recognize this but keep going.

R13AUD.original: ~z~There he is. Let's go talk to him. He's always at the games being held around Algonquin.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~那个就是。我们去跟他谈谈。他经常来Algonquin的赌局。

R13AUD.original: ~z~I think he's a bit freaked out. I guess he thought seeing you would answer some questions.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得他有点过于激动了，可能本来他觉得能从你这里问出更多的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~I'd be rich even if you weren't here. I'm an entrepreneur. Things would have taken off for me.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~就算你不来我也会很富。我是个企业家，早晚都会腾飞的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~How're we going to kidnap someone with that car? Get something bigger.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~How're we going to kidnap someone with that car? Get something bigger.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Alright, this isn't the normal route I take but keep going.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Alright, this isn't the normal route I take but keep going.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Hey Nicky. You've been a decent earner for me and I appreciate that. I'm throwing you a bone.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~喂Nicky。之前的活你都做得很棒，我很感谢。赏你一根骨头。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Don't be stupid, man. I know you are just taking us about in circles.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~别犯蠢，老兄。我知道你在带我们转圈圈。

R13AUD.original: ~z~I will find out where Darko Brevic is, and I will make him answer for his actions.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我会找出Darko Brevic的所在，让他为自己的行为付出代价。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Chill, cousin. If you go so fast we aren't going to find it.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Chill, cousin. If you go so fast we aren't going to find it.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Aaah! Are you crazy? This street's one way!
R13AUD.translated: ~z~啊！你疯了吗？这条路是单行线！

R13AUD.original: ~z~You really going to feel better once Florian is dead?
~z~Who set us up. It was you or Darko. I thought it must be him.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~背叛我们的人，不是你就是Darko了。我想一定是他。

R13AUD.original: ~z~There is no starting again. Darko Brevic may not be here in Liberty City, but he's still out there.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~There is no starting again. Darko Brevic may not be here in Liberty City, but he's still out there.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Slowly, slowly, catchy monkey, NB. We won't find him if you are racing.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Slowly, slowly, catchy monkey, NB. We won't find him if you are racing.

R13AUD.original: ~z~So I see... well it's great to see you guys... we must do brunch.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~咱懂了...见到你们还是很高兴的...有空吃顿饭。

R13AUD.original: ~z~There's some fanook called Talbot, Talbot Daniels, over in the Triangle.
~z~You trying to kill us? That traffic's heading toward us!
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你是想杀了我们吗？车子都在朝我们开！

R13AUD.original: ~z~You're a fucking loose cannon my friend.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你他妈也太反复无常了点吧，我的朋友。

R13AUD.original: ~z~He got away from us, NB. We're not going to be able to find Florian now.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~He got away from us, NB. We're not going to be able to find Florian now.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Cousin, I know you want to find him soon, but you must go slowly to do it.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Cousin, I know you want to find him soon, but you must go slowly to do it.

R13AUD.original: ~z~What're you doing? This is a one way street.
~z~Okay, you have to head on straight.
~z~Florian Cravic? I don't know what you're talking about.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Florian Cravic？我不知道你们在说什么。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Get in and don't try anything stupid, Talbot.
~z~I need to be alone now, Roman.
~z~I've come to ask you some questions.
~z~Shit, I would've chased him if I'd known you were so slow.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Shit, I would've chased him if I'd known you were so slow.

R13AUD.original: ~z~Shit NB, are you cranked on speed? We have to go slow to find the address.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Shit NB, are you cranked on speed? We have to go slow to find the address.

R13AUD.original: ~z~I been head to head with this guy a few times, NB. I know his tells. He's lying.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我和这人交手过几次，NB。我知道他的心思。他在说谎。

R13AUD.original: ~z~I have found Florian Cravic. There's a man called Talbot Daniels who will lead us to him.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我找到Florian Cravic了。有个叫Talbot Daniels的人会带我们去找他。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Something's gone wrong. I don't wanna talk about it.
~z~You think it was me... that's why you're here. You've come to kill me!
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你以为是咱...所以你才会来这儿。你是来杀咱的！

R13AUD.original: ~z~Here we are, this is Bernie's place. Can I go?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~Here we are, this is Bernie's place. Can I go?

R13AUD.original: ~z~Ray, I ain't gonna find the guy I'm after.
~z~Is not that, I'm coming to collect you from the apartment. Wait for me there.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~不是那个，我来公寓接你了。在那儿等我。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Have some fucking patience, Nicky. I thought you was wanting to find this rat.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~有点耐心，Nicky。我还以为你很想找到他的。

R13AUD.original: ~z~Help! You've taken a car down a one way street.
~z~Talbot, I know him from some of the card games I play.
~z~What are you guys doing here? Why did you kick my door down?
R13AUD.translated: ~z~你俩来这儿做什么？为什么你们要踹开咱的门？

R13AUD.original: ~z~All that has changed is that I am hunting one man instead of two...
R13AUD.translated: ~z~All that has changed is that I am hunting one man instead of two...

R13AUD.original: ~z~Now I am practically chopping board I have so many cuts on me.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~现在我已经是块砧板了，身上全是伤口。

R13AUD.original: ~z~I couldn't find Florian. Your man, Talbot, he was annoying the shit out of me.
R13AUD.translated: ~z~我找不到Florian。你的人Talbot他搞得我暴跳如雷。

R13AUD.original: ~z~So, you're finally going to kill Florian Cravic...
~z~We will find him, I promise you that.
